description:
Feature Description: Admin navigates to alert page,
     verifies all the sections are present
name: Advanced Filter

elements.name: Verify the advanced filter having 3 sections

steps.name: ITOps "admin" with username and password as "Itops_admin", "qa123" is in the home page
"Admin" enters project name as "Automation_IB_16" in the search field
"admin" clicks on project name "Automation_IB_16"
"admin" clicks on Alerts page
"admin" clicks on advanced filter icon
"admin" verifies heading as "Advanced Filters"
"admin" verifies Source and Resource section heading as "Source and Resources"
"admin" verifies State and Status,Date and Time sections heading as "State and Status" and "Date and Time"

elements.name: Verifying ITOps admin is able to apply the saved filter again

steps.name: "admin" enters source as "Solarwinds" and alert state as "Ticketed"
"admin" clicks on apply button
"admin" verifies user redirects to alert console
"admin" verifies the Data shown is solarwinds and ticketed alerts only
"admin" clicks on advanced filter icon
"admin" enters in last fields as "10" and select Duration type "Days"
"admin" clicks on apply button
"admin" verifies user redirects to alert console
"admin" verifies last "10" Days alerts are displayed in the console
"admin" verifies Remove all button is present

elements.name: Verify that user is able to view edit and delete option in Advanced Filter section

steps.name: "admin" clicks on advanced filter icon
"admin" clicks on Edit icon for "Automation" filter
"admin" verifies that edit and delete options are present
"admin" edits "ITSM" filter criteria
"admin" click on Update and Apply
"admin" clicks on Yes on confirmation pop up
"admin" verifies "Filter updated successfully." shown
"admin" verifies data in UI
"admin" clicks on advanced filter icon
"admin" clicks on Delete icon for "Automation" filter
"admin" clicks on Yes on confirmation pop up
"admin" verifies "Filter deleted successfully." shown
"admin" verifies deleted "Automation" filter is removed from the filter dropdown in console
"admin" clicks on logout button
